            "content": "<p>To keep your Ridhi Block Print pieces looking beautiful for years, please follow these care tips:<br/><br/>1. Machine Washable – Wash on a gentle cycle with cold water.<br/>2. Mild Detergent – Protect natural fibers and preserve colors.<br/>3. Do Not Bleach – Avoid harsh chemicals.<br/>4. Tumble Dry Low or Air Dry – Air drying recommended for longevity.<br/>5. Ironing – Iron on low while fabric is slightly damp, always on reverse side.<br/>6. Storage – Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</p>",
